paper_metadata.title: MAIN TEXT
paper_metadata.extraction_summary: Extracted variants in the BRCA2 gene, including clinical significance, penetrance data, and individual records.

functional_data.summary: Pathogenic variant associated with increased cancer risk.

variants.additional_notes: Identified in the context of population screening.
key_quotes: Altogether, the AF for the BRCA1/BRCA2 P/LP variants according to ClinVar in the unselected populations of 1076 patients in a genetically homogenous Polish population was 0.42%.
We identified 9 P/LP BRCA1/BRCA2 variants in the unselected Polish population.
